    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en-US">SemiFertile(x) ← FemaleSemiFertile(x)</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en-US">if x is a &apos;female semi-fertile&apos; then x is a &apos;semi fertile&apos;</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
    <skos:example xml:lang="en-US">Example of a &apos;female semi-fertile&apos;.</skos:example>
